SetInCountry: Indonesia
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Halim Mawardi Raharusun
AuthorCountry: Indonesia
Text: 'Prudential RideLondon 2018


  Prudential RideLondon is the biggest regularly cycling event in the world, which
  is Prudential be a main sponsorship for this event. Prudential as big insurance
  company in the world have a operate in many continen (asia, europe, afrika).

  i am so lucky because i am work at Prudential indonesia so because of that i have
  opportunies to join in Prudential RideLondon.


  Prudential RideLondon event always invite 2 people from every local bussiness unit
  in asia (indonesia, north korea, malaysia, singapore, etc) for join in this event.

  and you know what? i got one free ticket for joint in this event, thanks GOD.


  i am so verry happy because this is for the first time too i am going abroad, ha
  ha


  after i got good news from HR dept, i am try to get preparation , (cycling practice,
  dokumen preparation, etc)

  i am so verry happy


  12 july 2018 i go from jakarta to london

  after get flight around about 12 hours i get arrived in heathrow london


  after landing in heathrow london i am go to london backpacker in hendon,


  19 july 2018 , this time i have join as participant the biggest cycling event in
  the world

  i must cycling 80 miles start from buckingham palace go to surrey and then finish
  in buckingham


  and i am soo verry happy because i have already finished that race.


  thanks Prudential'
